OL,3,CWhere are the local elections
OL,4,Chappening around the North West?
OL,6,FPolling stations have opened across
OL,7,Flarge parts of the North West as
OL,8,Fpeople prepare to cast their vote in
OL,9,Fthe local elections.
OL,11,FCounts are taking place across 21
OL,12,Fcouncil areas, including every borough
OL,13,Fof Greater Manchester, parts of the
OL,14,FLiverpool City Region, and parts of
OL,15,FLancashire.
OL,17,FMost of these have a third of their
OL,18,Fcouncil seats up for grabs - while
OL,19,FSefton and St Helens are all out
OL,20,Felections.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
