OL,3,CWhere are the local elections
OL,4,Chappening around the North West?
OL,6,FWhere are council elections taking
OL,7,Fplace in the North West?
OL,9,FWhen will we know the results?
OL,11,FPolling stations will be open from 7
OL,12,Fam to 10 pm - and then counting will
OL,13,Fbegin.
OL,15,FAround a third of councils in England
OL,16,Fare due to declare their results
OL,17,Fovernight, in the North West that will
OL,18,Fbe Stockport, Oldham, Wigan, Salford,
OL,19,FChorley, Bolton and Tameside.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
