CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778186660
OL,3,CWhere are the local elections
OL,4,Chappening around the North West?
OL,6,FThe rest of the results will be
OL,7,Fdeclared from noon on Friday 8th May.
OL,9,FWhat happens next?
OL,11,FIf a political party holds more than
OL,12,Fhalf of the seats on each council,
OL,13,Fthey will run the council and key
OL,14,Flocal services.
OL,16,FIf no party has an outright majority,
OL,17,Fthen a council is deemed to be "under
OL,18,Fno overall control".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
