OL,3,CWhere are the local elections
OL,4,Chappening around the North West?
OL,6,FWhen that happens, councils can agree
OL,7,Fto a minority administration, where
OL,8,Fthe party with the largest number of
OL,9,Fcouncil seats takes charge.
OL,10,FAlternatively, some of the smaller
OL,11,Fpolitical parties can form coalitions
OL,12,Fand lead together.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
